Tight integration for mvapich-2 was tested with version
mvapich2-1.7-r5225.

Building mvapich2
=================
No special options are needed for configuration and build of mvapich2.
Grid Engine tight integration is enabled by default.

Installing the PE
=================
qconf -Ap $SGE_ROOT/mpi/mvapich2/mvapich2.template

